4. Run the 1.01 patch included in the Crack dir.
5. Copy over the cracked content from the Crack dir on DVD2 to your &lt;install&gt;bin dir, overwriting any existing files.
6. Play the game.
7. Support the software developers. If you like this game, BUY IT!                                   

